Class Point

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Point

  • public final class Point

extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a Point with x and y coordinates. Point objects are immutable. (Compare to java.awt.Point which is mutable)
    Version:
    Autumn 2016
    Author:
